# nsite / Nostr deploy — key material & signer config. NEVER commit:
# this is a PUBLIC repo; a leaked nsec or bunker secret is permanent
# and unrecoverable. Any non-secret deploy config is force-added
# deliberately, only after verifying it carries no secret.
.nsite/
.nsite-cli/
*.nsec
nostr-key*
*nsec*
*.bunker
bunker*.json
.env
.env.*

# Personal egym Wellpass tooling — the scrape source and the HTML parser
# stay strictly off the remote. Only the curated, anonymised match
# results (tools/wellpass.json) are committed. Patterns cover both
# accidental placement inside the repo and common artifact names.
/wellpass-matcher/
wellpass-matcher/
wellpass-latest.html
wellpass-*.html
wellpass-names-*.json
wellpass-vs-boards.md
wellpass-vs-boards-*.json
wellpass-match.mjs
